hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted intercept pharma uk & ireland The Deck is made for partying, and its big sound overreaches for such a compact device. Outdoor mode pumps up the mid- and high-range sound, but in both indoor and outdoor settings bass is lacking. The 360-degree sound claim the manufacturers make is less a function of highfalutin' virtual surround sound as it is a practical assessment of the positioning of the speaker channels: seated on its base, the speaker throws sound up and around.
